<span class="title">How We Use Your Information</span>
  <p>
  <b>Anonymous Information</b>
  </p><p>
  &#149 Anonymous Information cannot be tied to personally indentifiable information. We use this information to improve our site. This information helps us focus our resources on the features that are most popular with our customers.
  </p><p>
  <i>It is quite possible that we will share non-identifiable aggregated demographic information with our partners and advertisers. For example, we may tell an advertiser that a specific number of customers visited an area on our web site, but we will not disclose anything that could be used to identify individuals.</i>
  </p><p>
  <b>Personally Identifiable Information</b>
  </p><p>
  &#149 Registration Information: If you are providing personally identifiable information on a registration page (such as Customer's Toolbox on www.sheahomes.com) it will be used solely to respond to your inquiries unless we indicate that it may be shared with other Shea affiliated companies or selected outside vendors. If we indicate such sharing you will be given the opportunity to decline such use.
  </p><p>
  &#149 Request Information: If you are providing personally identifiable information on a request for information or services page, such as Contact Us! Or Notify Me! We will use this information only to reply to your request in that category. For example, if you register to be notified when community information will be available, we will send periodic e-mails to notify you of that information. We do not share email lists outside our affiliated companies unless we tell you that in advance and provide you the opportunity to decline such use.
  </p><p>
  <i>We do not sell or make your information available to marketing agencies or outside parties unless we advise you in advance and provide you the opportunity to decline such use.</i>